&lt;p&gt;The Estates Department is responsible for the repair, maintenance and management of all Building and Engineering Services within the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for experienced Contractor Escorts to join our Estates Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holders will have Contractor Escort experience and will be responsible for the safety and security of contractors, workman and service engineers on site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although primarily based at Roseberry Park Hospital, Middlesbrough you may be required to work from other Trust sites for periods of time as the service dictates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Graham Nellis Building Estates Officer on graham.nellis@nhs.net 01642 424499 or 07825355905&lt;/p&gt;
